this project is a simulation to the payment proccess using the c language 

compossed of 3 stages
1-card
2-terminal 
3-server

in card it gets :
holder name 
exp date
pan number

in terminal it checks :
all the card data are avilable
if the pan number is according to lhun algorithm
is the card expired 
it requests the transaction amount and checks if it is not exceeding the terminal max amount

in the server :
it checks if the account valid in the data base 
it checks if the ammount is sufficient under the account
it executes the payment proccess 
it updates the database and prints a payment receite
